<br>
People who chose a deity <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *CAN*</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> change their faction through hard work, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> but</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> people who chose AGNOSTIC have <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> NO</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> way to change their ability to wear deity-restricted items.<br>
